13 January 2020 Members of the media who have applied for accreditation to cover the official funeral of Dr Richard Maponya are advised to collect their accreditation cards as follows: Date: Monday, 13 January 2020         Time: 08h00 – 16h00Venue: University of Johannesburg, Soweto Campus NB: Members of the media are advised to bring along their ID’s and press cards on the collection of accreditation. For more information regarding accreditation contact:Mr Ishmael SelemaleCell: 072 637 7665E-mail: ishmael@gcis.gov.za Issued: Government Communication and Information System (GCIS) 